name: Promoclean™ TP 1113
description: Promoclean™ TP 1113 is specifically formulated for the removal of hydrocarbon- or water-based oils and greases in an aqueous immersion process. Despite having a high pH to facilitate cleaning, it does not harm sensitive metals or alloys such as titanium, aluminum, copper, or brass. It is a concentrated product that must be diluted with DI water before use.
